messages.msgSnippet: Jennifer, Over here in Brevard county I belong to a homeschool group that is made up mostly of unschoolers. So, we are remotely near you. Denese in Palm
messages.messageBody:
"Jennifer,
Over here in Brevard county I belong to a homeschool group that is made up mostly of unschoolers. So, we are "remotely" near you.
Denese
in Palm Bay"


Denese~

Where is Palm Bay in relationship to Cape Canaveral? That's the only area I really know of Brevard. My brother lives there. Oh, yeah, and the zoo.......
I am envious that you have a group of unschoolers. I don't know any.

Peace~

Jennifer




I'll carry your books, I'll carry a tune,
I'll carry on, carry over, carry forward,
Cary Grant, cash & carry, Carry Me Back To Old Virginia,
I'll even Hara Kari if you show me how,
but I will *not* carry a gun.
- Hawkeye, M*A*S*H
